# Claude Code Action - Project Overview

## Project Purpose
This is a **GitHub Action that integrates Claude AI with GitHub repositories**. It's a fork of the official Claude Code Action that adds OAuth authentication support for Claude Max subscribers.

## Key Features
- 🤖 Interactive code assistant that responds to comments
- 🔍 Code review and analysis capabilities  
- ✨ Code implementation and fixes
- 💬 PR/Issue integration via comments
- 🛠️ Flexible tool access and GitHub API integration
- 📋 Progress tracking with dynamic checkboxes
- 🔐 Multiple authentication methods (OAuth, Anthropic API, Bedrock, Vertex AI)

## Main Entry Points
- [action.yml](mdc:action.yml) - GitHub Action configuration and workflow definition
- [src/entrypoints/prepare.ts](mdc:src/entrypoints/prepare.ts) - Action preparation and context setup
- [src/entrypoints/update-comment-link.ts](mdc:src/entrypoints/update-comment-link.ts) - Comment updating logic

## Project Structure
- `src/` - Main source code directory
  - `entrypoints/` - GitHub Action entry points
  - `github/` - GitHub API integrations
  - `mcp/` - Model Context Protocol implementations
  - `create-prompt/` - Prompt generation logic
- `test/` - Test files using Bun test framework
- `examples/` - GitHub workflow examples for different use cases
- `scripts/` - Build and development scripts

